---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Berhasil Disimpan" description="Form identitas lembaga berhasil disimpan.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0B0F19] flex flex-col font-poppins relative selection:bg-indigo-500/30">
    <!-- Dekorasi Background -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none z-0">
        <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 dark:bg-indigo-500/5 blur-[100px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 dark:bg-emerald-500/5 blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="relative z-50 w-full bg-white/70 dark:bg-[#111827]/70 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 sticky top-0">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-violet-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-lg font-black font-outfit text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight">Berhasil</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="relative z-10 flex-1 w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[60vh]">
        
        <div class="flex-col items-center justify-center text-center w-full bg-white dark:bg-[#111827] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/5 relative overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Background Decoration for Card -->
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 via-purple-500 to-emerald-500"></div>

            <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-500 mb-6 relative">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full animate-ping bg-emerald-400 opacity-20"></div>
                <svg class="w-12 h-12 relative z-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black font-outfit text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-4">Data Tersimpan!</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8 text-base">Profil dan Identitas Lembaga telah berhasil diperbarui ke dalam sistem. Demi keamanan, sesi form dan token sebelumnya telah dihancurkan.</p>

            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-500/20 text-left">
                <div class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                    PROSES SELANJUTNYA:
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-sm text-indigo-900/80 dark:text-indigo-200/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                    Silakan hubungi Administrator untuk melanjutkan ke tahap berikutnya:
                </p>
                
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-500/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Kirimkan file <b>Kop Surat</b>, <b>Logo Sekolah</b>, <b>Stempel</b>, dan <b>Tanda Tangan Kepsek</b> ke Admin.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-500/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Isi data kelulusan Siswa beserta Nilai secara mandiri di template yang diberikan.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-200 dark:bg-indigo-500/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Upload File Deploy ke Hosting (Akan dibantu oleh tim Administrator).</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">
                    Sesi form publik ini telah berakhir. Anda dapat menutup tab browser ini.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
